---
---
<section id="about" class="relative grain px-8 md:px-16 py-20" style="background:#FEF8EA; overflow:hidden;">
  <!-- decorative large background text -->
  <div class="absolute top-8 right-8 pointer-events-none select-none" style="font-family:'Pacifico',cursive; font-size:clamp(5rem,18vw,14rem); color:rgba(254,164,159,0.12); line-height:1; z-index:0;">
    Lowell
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <div class="np-label"><span>About</span></div>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Pacifico',cursive; font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.2rem); color:#101357; line-height:1.15;">
        Lowell George
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-14 items-start">
      <!-- Quote block -->
      <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
        <blockquote style="border-left: 4px solid #fea49f; padding-left:1.5rem; margin:0 0 2rem 0;">
          <p style="font-size:1.2rem; line-height:1.8; color:#2a1f1f; font-style:italic;">
            "He was The Doctor. His was the private inspiration for their more public triumph."
          </p>
        </blockquote>
        <p style="font-size:1rem; line-height:1.85; color:#444; margin-bottom:1.2rem;">
          His enthusiasm for the musical success of others was an infectious empowerment, as overwhelming as the subtle downturned eyebrow of his disapproval. He pushed us past ourselves, through doors we never knew were there, to that place where the Wolf was alive, and there was no jive.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:1rem; line-height:1.85; color:#444; margin-bottom:2rem;">
          He went on to fill the big shoes of Little Feat, and we all knew what he would become. Except he didn't.
        </p>
        <p style="font-family:'Roboto Condensed',sans-serif; font-size:0.75rem; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#f04a53;">
          — Martin Kibee
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10" style="display:inline-block; border: 2px dashed #f9a84d; padding: 14px 24px;">
          <p style="font-family:'Roboto Condensed',sans-serif; font-size:0.75rem; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#101357; margin:0;">
            Music Licensing · Motion Pictures · Covers
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo + video -->
      <div style="flex-shrink:0; width:100%; max-width:280px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1.5rem;">
        <div style="position:relative;">
          <img
            src="/57164060_10218471484436280_6625553805079478272_n.jpg"
            alt="Lowell George"
            style="width:100%; display:block; border:4px solid #fea49f; box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 #FFE940;"
          />
        </div>
        <div style="position:relative; padding-bottom:56.25%; height:0; overflow:hidden; border:3px dashed #44a4f2;">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmike.jacobus.7%2Fvideos%2F10213979804921116%2F&show_text=false&width=280"
            style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:none;"
            allowfullscreen
            allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
